to meet Zhang Hao on September 20th

556
00:28:10,310 --> 00:28:12,680
and also actually met Zhang Hao

557
00:28:13,310 --> 00:28:14,640
at the entrance of NTUH.

558
00:28:15,680 --> 00:28:17,610
What does this have to do
with this Mr. Lin?

559
00:28:17,610 --> 00:28:19,820
I suspect that the person Zhang Hao met

560
00:28:20,140 --> 00:28:22,870
at Sanrong Trading in September
was Lin Yiliang.

561
00:28:23,050 --> 00:28:25,420
And according to Liu Kangfu,

562
00:28:25,720 --> 00:28:27,740
these two had a deep connection.

563
00:28:28,720 --> 00:28:29,880
I believe

564
00:28:30,550 --> 00:28:32,540
they might be brothers

565
00:28:33,000 --> 00:28:33,770
or

566
00:28:34,500 --> 00:28:37,980
Communist spy partners
having worked together for a long time.

567
00:28:37,980 --> 00:28:39,880
But regardless of their relationship,

568
00:28:39,880 --> 00:28:41,490
as long as we investigate him thoroughly,

569
00:28:41,490 --> 00:28:44,110
it will lead to a major breakthrough
in the case.

570
00:28:44,110 --> 00:28:46,040
Birds of a feather flock together.

571
00:28:46,310 --> 00:28:47,570
This kind of situation

572
00:28:48,680 --> 00:28:49,610
is quite common.

573
00:28:50,740 --> 00:28:51,670
It's not enough.

574
00:28:53,090 --> 00:28:54,620
It's still too peripheral.

575
00:28:54,680 --> 00:28:57,010
Since you're suspecting Deputy Chief Wu,

576
00:28:57,030 --> 00:28:59,980
you must get the first-hand information.

577
00:29:00,150 --> 00:29:01,870
Yes, sir. I'm working on it.

578
00:29:02,870 --> 00:29:04,830
Where else can we
find such a good employer

579
00:29:04,830 --> 00:29:06,110
who even works alongside us?

580
00:29:06,110 --> 00:29:09,310
Anywhere else,
we'd have to carry everything ourselves.

581
00:29:14,270 --> 00:29:15,600
What are you looking at?

582
00:29:16,140 --> 00:29:17,030
Keep working.

583
00:29:17,120 --> 00:29:18,720
I've been working all along.

584
00:29:18,870 --> 00:29:21,470
The sooner you finish,
the sooner you get paid.

585
00:29:30,530 --> 00:29:31,790
Just put it by the door.

586
00:29:43,090 --> 00:29:44,290
Put it by the door too.

587
00:29:44,680 --> 00:29:46,620
Hello. What are you doing?

588
00:29:46,960 --> 00:29:47,990
I need to use the restroom.

589
00:29:47,990 --> 00:29:48,840
Wait.

590
00:29:49,740 --> 00:29:50,310
This way, please.

591
00:29:50,310 --> 00:29:51,510
No, the one inside...

592
00:29:56,200 --> 00:29:58,860
Turn left here,
and you'll find it to your right.

593
00:30:08,590 --> 00:30:11,450
The staff in the shop are very vigilant.

594
00:30:12,070 --> 00:30:14,180
And they're also very tight-lipped.

595
00:30:14,610 --> 00:30:15,980
I've been looking for a chance,

596
00:30:15,980 --> 00:30:17,740
but I couldn't even get one foot inside.

597
00:30:17,740 --> 00:30:18,310
Leader,

598
00:30:21,320 --> 00:30:22,230
I think

599
00:30:23,320 --> 00:30:26,060
there's definitely something fishy
about the shop.

600
00:30:26,060 --> 00:30:27,740
Alright, let me sum this up for you.

601
00:30:27,740 --> 00:30:28,640
So with an ordinary identity,

602
00:30:28,640 --> 00:30:30,170
you can't go inside, right?

603
00:30:31,640 --> 00:30:32,310
Yes.

604
00:30:34,500 --> 00:30:35,650
I think

605
00:30:36,180 --> 00:30:37,110
Sanrong Trading

606
00:30:38,140 --> 00:30:39,610
is impenetrable

607
00:30:39,640 --> 00:30:40,770
and sealed off.

608
00:30:41,980 --> 00:30:43,070
For us to break in

609
00:30:43,440 --> 00:30:44,970
is indeed quite difficult.

610
00:30:46,940 --> 00:30:48,720
How many Keelung Work Committee members

611
00:30:48,720 --> 00:30:49,780
we arrested for the Guangming News case

612
00:30:49,780 --> 00:30:51,480
are still in custody?

613
00:30:52,980 --> 00:30:54,440
About 30.

614
00:30:56,140 --> 00:30:57,550
About 30.

615
00:30:58,880 --> 00:31:00,350
You mean

616
00:31:01,140 --> 00:31:04,470
we'll pretend to be
from the Keelung Work Committee, right?

617
00:31:06,090 --> 00:31:07,690
That's a great idea, Leader.

618
00:31:13,610 --> 00:31:15,140
I've been wrongly accused.

619
00:31:17,290 --> 00:31:18,300
I didn't do it!

620
00:31:24,380 --> 00:31:25,160
Please.

621
00:31:26,400 --> 00:31:27,380
Let me go!

622
00:31:31,980 --> 00:31:33,040
Please release me!

623
00:31:34,090 --> 00:31:35,220
It really wasn't me!

624
00:31:36,740 --> 00:31:37,530
Mr. Zhuang.

625
00:31:42,930 --> 00:31:44,190
It has been a long time.

626
00:31:46,500 --> 00:31:47,630
You've lost weight.

627
00:31:56,070 --> 00:31:56,770
No, no, no.

628
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:00,000
You bastard.

629
00:32:03,810 --> 00:32:05,140
Forty-seven lives lost

630
00:32:07,380 --> 00:32:09,140
at Keelung Middle School.

631
00:32:11,960 --> 00:32:13,550
Can you sleep at night?

632
00:32:15,490 --> 00:32:16,330
Yes, I can.

633
00:32:17,070 --> 00:32:19,570
You know, I'm also a materialist.

634
00:32:21,190 --> 00:32:22,880
You'll die a terrible death.

635
00:32:26,570 --> 00:32:29,170
It really is suitable.

636
00:32:36,980 --> 00:32:37,780
Bring him out.

637
00:32:45,480 --> 00:32:46,940
Let's stop here for today.

638
00:32:47,650 --> 00:32:49,310
Deputy Chief Wu, please stay.

639
00:32:57,740 --> 00:32:58,440
Senior.

640
00:32:59,140 --> 00:33:01,530
The Ministry of Foreign Affairs told me

641
00:33:02,140 --> 00:33:03,640
that the French government

642
00:33:03,640 --> 00:33:07,220
finally agreed to let Huang Jie's corps
withdraw to Vietnam.

643
00:33:09,180 --> 00:33:09,910
That's good.

644
00:33:11,480 --> 00:33:13,340
Better to get some back than none.

645
00:33:13,740 --> 00:33:15,600
It's better than letting Lin Biao

646
00:33:15,870 --> 00:33:17,430
capture 30,000 more men.

647
00:33:18,310 --> 00:33:19,240
The condition is

648
00:33:21,000 --> 00:33:23,180
that the troops
must surrender their weapons.

649
00:33:23,180 --> 00:33:24,510
Surrender the weapons?

650
00:33:25,570 --> 00:33:27,630
Surrender the weapons to the French?

651
00:33:34,670 --> 00:33:35,280
Come in.

652
00:33:42,050 --> 00:33:44,140
Leader, you wanted to see me?

653
00:33:44,910 --> 00:33:45,570
Have a seat.

654
00:33:50,440 --> 00:33:52,140
How has your harvest been lately?

655
00:33:52,140 --> 00:33:53,240
W-What harvest?

656
00:33:55,180 --> 00:33:56,070
I heard that

657
00:33:56,240 --> 00:33:59,880
you've been frequently helping out
at the Operations Division lately.

658
00:33:59,880 --> 00:34:00,570
Leader,

659
00:34:04,420 --> 00:34:05,850
I didn't keep it all to myself.

660
00:34:05,850 --> 00:34:07,350
While you were away,

661
00:34:07,800 --> 00:34:10,000
our colleagues were almost out of food.

662
00:34:10,840 --> 00:34:12,010
So I came up with a way

663
00:34:12,340 --> 00:34:14,739
to improve everyone's living conditions.

664
00:34:17,340 --> 00:34:19,630
Do you remember

665
00:34:19,630 --> 00:34:21,030
the full name of our team?

666
00:34:21,840 --> 00:34:24,130
The Counterintelligence Section
of the BIS.

667
00:34:24,130 --> 00:34:27,880
The Counterintelligence Section
of the BIS

668
00:34:28,270 --> 00:34:30,290
actually has a very short history.

669
00:34:30,980 --> 00:34:33,310
When you were still at the Taiwan station,

670
00:34:34,070 --> 00:34:36,800
it was just a unit
under the Operations Division.

671
00:34:39,280 --> 00:34:41,280
After the Guangming News case,

672
00:34:42,070 --> 00:34:44,590
the Director appreciated

673
00:34:44,820 --> 00:34:48,090
our competence
in capturing Communist spies,

674
00:34:48,280 --> 00:34:50,670
so he made our team a separate section.

675
00:34:52,130 --> 00:34:52,780
However,

676
00:34:53,030 --> 00:34:53,590
if

677
00:34:54,070 --> 00:34:56,340
our future work doesn't go smoothly

678
00:34:57,390 --> 00:34:59,400
and we fail to catch Communist spies,

679
00:34:59,400 --> 00:35:01,800
then I'm afraid you'll end up
on the streets

680
00:35:02,280 --> 00:35:03,080
checking IDs.

681
00:35:05,020 --> 00:35:06,270
Just as you said,

682
00:35:06,980 --> 00:35:10,840
"I speak both Mandarin and Hokkien,

683
00:35:10,840 --> 00:35:12,140
which comes in handy,

684
00:35:12,320 --> 00:35:15,590
while Yu Xiaonan is so inarticulate

685
00:35:15,590 --> 00:35:17,940
that he can't even check IDs properly."

686
00:35:19,490 --> 00:35:20,220
Leader,

687
00:35:21,360 --> 00:35:22,560
how did you know that?

688
00:35:22,710 --> 00:35:24,260
Isn't this what you said?

689
00:35:24,510 --> 00:35:26,640
I believe those were your exact words.

690
00:35:27,270 --> 00:35:28,330
I'm sorry, Leader.

691
00:35:28,760 --> 00:35:29,550
I...

692
00:35:31,940 --> 00:35:33,800
I was indeed speaking out of turn.

693
00:35:34,030 --> 00:35:35,830
How is that speaking out of turn?

694
00:35:36,360 --> 00:35:38,050
It was precisely
because you have these skills

695
00:35:38,050 --> 00:35:39,630
that I specifically transferred you here

696
00:35:39,630 --> 00:35:40,820
from Director Ye.

697
00:35:41,050 --> 00:35:43,050
You're overthinking it. It's fine.

698
00:35:43,190 --> 00:35:43,830
Sit down.

699
00:35:48,030 --> 00:35:48,840
Even if

700
00:35:49,450 --> 00:35:50,810
the Ministry of Defense

701
00:35:51,850 --> 00:35:54,670
orders Huang Jie's corps
not to surrender their weapons

702
00:35:54,670 --> 00:35:56,070
and hold their position,

703
00:35:56,070 --> 00:35:57,800
do you think they would listen?

704
00:35:58,980 --> 00:36:00,440
They've fled all the way from Hunan,

705
00:36:00,440 --> 00:36:02,110
running over 1,000 kilometers.

706
00:36:02,110 --> 00:36:04,210
They're just one step away
from crossing the border

707
00:36:04,210 --> 00:36:05,170
to safety.

708
00:36:06,050 --> 00:36:06,940
Huang Jie's corps

709
00:36:06,940 --> 00:36:09,650
had been retreating
under the PLA's pursuit.

710
00:36:09,920 --> 00:36:11,500
They could only detour through Vietnam

711
00:36:11,500 --> 00:36:12,680
to return to Taiwan.

712
00:36:13,940 --> 00:36:15,710
Wu Shi had approached Zhou Zhirou
several times before

713
00:36:15,710 --> 00:36:17,640
but failed to get any information.

714
00:36:17,710 --> 00:36:20,570
Now that Zhou Zhirou brought up
the matter himself,

715
00:36:20,780 --> 00:36:22,260
Wu Shi keenly realized

716
00:36:22,500 --> 00:36:24,710
this was the perfect opportunity
to pry into the air force's

717
00:36:24,710 --> 00:36:25,770
secret operation.

718
00:36:26,700 --> 00:36:29,320
Wu Shi then seized the chance,

719
00:36:29,860 --> 00:36:31,900
using his opposition to Huang Jie's corps

720
00:36:31,900 --> 00:36:34,230
surrendering their weapons to the French

721
00:36:34,380 --> 00:36:37,420
to probe Zhou Zhirou's true thoughts
on the matter

722
00:36:38,260 --> 00:36:40,380
and then act accordingly.

723
00:36:42,030 --> 00:36:43,630
In any case, it's better than

724
00:36:44,600 --> 00:36:46,670
being annihilated
by the Communist Army, isn't it?

725
00:36:46,670 --> 00:36:47,500
Chief,

726
00:36:48,920 --> 00:36:50,250
what are you going to do?

727
00:36:51,690 --> 00:36:53,440
After Huang Jie's corps
surrender their weapons,

728
00:36:53,440 --> 00:36:56,860
they'll assemble and stand by
in Haiphong, Vietnam.

729
00:36:58,840 --> 00:37:02,190
This involves many parties.

730
00:37:03,060 --> 00:37:03,730
Therefore,

731
00:37:03,880 --> 00:37:06,340
someone from our ministry
must take charge.

732
00:37:07,030 --> 00:37:08,440
I'll have to trouble you

733
00:37:08,880 --> 00:37:10,940
to coordinate with various parties.

734
00:37:12,650 --> 00:37:13,190
Yes.

735
00:37:13,760 --> 00:37:14,560
I understand.

736
00:37:15,340 --> 00:37:16,740
I'll take charge of this.

737
00:37:17,080 --> 00:37:18,680
I'll report directly to you.

738
00:37:19,370 --> 00:37:20,230
For 30,000 men,

739
00:37:21,460 --> 00:37:22,650
I need transport ships.

740
00:37:22,650 --> 00:37:24,310
I've made a rough estimation.

741
00:37:24,500 --> 00:37:25,500
In total,

742
00:37:26,200 --> 00:37:27,930
we need 3 to 10 transport ships.

743
00:37:28,480 --> 00:37:29,070
Good.

744
00:37:29,880 --> 00:37:31,810
You can go
to Director Ma directly.

745
00:37:32,110 --> 00:37:35,640
He is currently in charge
of coordinating military logistics.

746
00:37:35,840 --> 00:37:39,170
If it's really impossible
to arrange the ships,

747
00:37:40,150 --> 00:37:41,880
then we'll have to postpone it.

748
00:37:42,980 --> 00:37:44,310
It cannot be postponed.

749
00:37:44,940 --> 00:37:45,610
Chief.

750
00:37:47,610 --> 00:37:50,740
Huang Jie was the former
Deputy Chief of Staff after all.

751
00:37:51,480 --> 00:37:52,880
If he's really captured,

752
00:37:53,650 --> 00:37:55,650
it'll be embarrassing for all of us.

753
00:37:57,440 --> 00:37:59,570
If we can bring back Huang Jie's corps,

754
00:38:00,120 --> 00:38:02,850
that's 30,000 combat-ready soldiers
after all.

755
00:38:05,980 --> 00:38:06,650
Good.

756
00:38:09,420 --> 00:38:11,800
Then I'll trouble you with this task.

757
00:38:13,030 --> 00:38:14,760
Rest assured. I'll do my best.

758
00:38:14,980 --> 00:38:16,510
I will definitely work hard

759
00:38:17,190 --> 00:38:19,280
and catch more Communist spies for you,

760
00:38:19,280 --> 00:38:22,150
making the Counterintelligence Section
live up to its name.

761
00:38:22,150 --> 00:38:24,070
It's not for me.

762
00:38:24,070 --> 00:38:25,980
Even if you don't say doing it
for our party and our ideology,

763
00:38:25,980 --> 00:38:27,340
you should at least mention doing it

764
00:38:27,340 --> 00:38:29,650
for the welfare of everyone
in our section.

765
00:38:29,650 --> 00:38:30,910
You just said yourself

766
00:38:31,440 --> 00:38:34,370
that you're concerned
about our colleagues' livelihoods.

767
00:38:34,370 --> 00:38:35,100
That's good.

768
00:38:35,900 --> 00:38:39,240
Yes, sir! I'll catch more Communist spies
for our section.

769
00:38:39,300 --> 00:38:39,940
Good.

770
00:38:43,260 --> 00:38:44,120
Weng Lianwang,

771
00:38:44,940 --> 00:38:46,440
I have a mission right now

772
00:38:46,880 --> 00:38:48,150
for you to carry out.

773
00:38:58,000 --> 00:39:00,060
Director Ma, Deputy Chief Wu is here.

774
00:39:01,880 --> 00:39:04,570
Deputy Chief Wu, what brings you here?

775
00:39:05,480 --> 00:39:07,880
Director Ma, what a refined hobby
you have.

776
00:39:08,150 --> 00:39:11,300
Doing this in front of you is really
showing off my poor skills to an expert.

777
00:39:11,300 --> 00:39:12,830
It's just a way to kill time.

778
00:39:13,980 --> 00:39:14,980
This is really something.

779
00:39:14,980 --> 00:39:15,690
Luo Zhenyu.

780
00:39:16,440 --> 00:39:17,910
You're truly an expert.

781
00:39:19,110 --> 00:39:19,800
Sir,

782
00:39:20,420 --> 00:39:22,380
when will you also write
a piece of calligraphy for me?

783
00:39:22,380 --> 00:39:24,000
Director Duan got
a piece of your calligraphy

784
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:25,530
and keeps showing it off to me.

785
00:39:25,530 --> 00:39:26,480
No problem.

786
00:39:27,880 --> 00:39:31,020
Just tell me what content you want,
and I'll write it for you.

787
00:39:31,020 --> 00:39:32,490
Please, have a seat.

788
00:39:33,300 --> 00:39:34,530
You're a great scholar

789
00:39:34,530 --> 00:39:36,150
and also a master calligrapher.

790
00:39:36,150 --> 00:39:38,350
Anything you write would be wonderful.

791
00:39:40,760 --> 00:39:41,480
Please.

792
00:39:44,260 --> 00:39:45,060
Have some tea.

793
00:39:47,570 --> 00:39:48,480
Recently,

794
00:39:48,980 --> 00:39:49,980
I managed to get

795
00:39:49,980 --> 00:39:52,730
some precious calligraphy supplies
from Guangzhou.

796
00:39:52,730 --> 00:39:54,480
The rice paper is from Jingxian.

797
00:39:54,480 --> 00:39:55,880
And among them, there was

798
00:39:56,480 --> 00:39:57,810
a Wushi Qiyan ink stick.

799
00:39:57,980 --> 00:39:58,780
That ink stick

800
00:39:59,940 --> 00:40:00,880
is truly rare.

801
00:40:02,530 --> 00:40:03,990
I've already sent someone

802
00:40:04,480 --> 00:40:06,140
to deliver it to Wu's Mansion.

803
00:40:07,940 --> 00:40:09,270
Thank you, Director Ma.

804
00:40:12,070 --> 00:40:13,400
Rice paper is precious,

805
00:40:13,480 --> 00:40:15,540
but soldiers are even more valuable.

806
00:40:15,940 --> 00:40:17,870
Director Ma, you must have guessed

807
00:40:18,380 --> 00:40:19,650
that I came here today

808
00:40:20,240 --> 00:40:22,850
to request your help to bring

809
00:40:23,020 --> 00:40:24,350
Huang Jie's corps back.

810
00:40:24,900 --> 00:40:27,200
Sir, I wouldn't dare call it a request.

811
00:40:28,190 --> 00:40:30,120
The Chief has already informed me.

812
00:40:30,130 --> 00:40:31,160
I was planning

813
00:40:31,190 --> 00:40:32,380
to go to your office later

814
00:40:32,380 --> 00:40:33,480
to report to you personally.

815
00:40:33,480 --> 00:40:35,480
Then I'll get straight to the point.

816
00:40:36,880 --> 00:40:38,640
There are 30,000 men in Huang Jie's corps.

817
00:40:38,640 --> 00:40:41,640
We need at least five transport ships.

818
00:40:42,260 --> 00:40:44,590
You're really putting me
in a difficult position.

819
00:40:44,590 --> 00:40:46,450
Even if you pushed me to the limit,

820
00:40:46,510 --> 00:40:48,620
I still couldn't produce
five transport ships.

821
00:40:48,620 --> 00:40:49,620
That's not right.

822
00:40:50,760 --> 00:40:51,500
I know

823
00:40:51,800 --> 00:40:54,940
that the military aid from the U.S. alone

824
00:40:54,940 --> 00:40:57,150
included ten transport ships.

825
00:40:57,300 --> 00:40:59,840
My request isn't unreasonable.

826
00:40:59,860 --> 00:41:01,170
Sir,

827
00:41:02,610 --> 00:41:04,480
I'm just in charge of logistics.

828
00:41:04,690 --> 00:41:07,090
There are too many transport requests now.

829
00:41:07,110 --> 00:41:09,000
I really can't spare any
to allocate to you.

830
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:10,260
Then what should we do?

831
00:41:10,980 --> 00:41:11,690
We just let

832
00:41:12,340 --> 00:41:13,690
the 30,000 soldiers of Huang Jie's corps

833
00:41:13,690 --> 00:41:15,870
wait in that internment camp in Vietnam?

834
00:41:15,870 --> 00:41:18,150
Every few days, more than ten bodies
are carried out.

835
00:41:18,150 --> 00:41:19,480
This involves

836
00:41:20,110 --> 00:41:21,260
diplomatic affairs

837
00:41:21,440 --> 00:41:22,750
and the image
of the Nationalist Government.

838
00:41:22,750 --> 00:41:24,690
Director Ma,
can you bear the consequences?

839
00:41:24,690 --> 00:41:25,480
Sir,

840
00:41:26,690 --> 00:41:27,570
how about this?

841
00:41:28,480 --> 00:41:30,440
I'll allocate three ships to you first.

842
00:41:30,440 --> 00:41:30,980
Would that work?

843
00:41:30,980 --> 00:41:33,100
Director Ma, since this is so difficult
for you,

844
00:41:33,100 --> 00:41:35,020
then just take back the rice paper

845
00:41:35,210 --> 00:41:37,540
and other things you sent to my residence.

846
00:41:38,650 --> 00:41:41,180
If I can't bring back
General Huang's troops,

847
00:41:41,400 --> 00:41:42,800
I won't have many chances

848
00:41:42,820 --> 00:41:44,950
to use such fine paper and ink anymore.

849
00:41:45,260 --> 00:41:45,980
Sir,

850
00:41:46,190 --> 00:41:47,480
please don't leave.

851
00:41:49,150 --> 00:41:50,260
Let me be honest.

852
00:41:50,760 --> 00:41:53,500
I just can't make bricks without straw.

853
00:41:54,190 --> 00:41:56,620
Commander-in-Chief Xue Yue
borrowed the ships

854
00:41:56,620 --> 00:41:57,690
to march forward into Hainan Island

855
00:41:57,690 --> 00:41:58,980
and hasn't returned them yet.

856
00:41:58,980 --> 00:42:01,530
Chief Gu sent a fleet to Guangxi

857
00:42:01,530 --> 00:42:03,480
to pick up Bai Chongxi's troops.

858
00:42:03,610 --> 00:42:04,440
And Chief Zhou

859
00:42:04,460 --> 00:42:06,980
dispatched many transport ships

860
00:42:07,410 --> 00:42:08,460
to Zhoushan.

861
00:42:08,940 --> 00:42:10,210
I don't even have enough ships

862
00:42:10,210 --> 00:42:12,210
to send supplies to Kinmen.

863
00:42:12,230 --> 00:42:13,690
I hope you can understand.

864
00:42:14,300 --> 00:42:15,990
Please, have a seat.

865
00:42:19,000 --> 00:42:21,690
General Hu Lian
has already urged me twice.

866
00:42:25,030 --> 00:42:26,690
Sending supplies to Zhoushan

867
00:42:26,940 --> 00:42:28,440
isn't that urgent, is it?

868
00:42:29,480 --> 00:42:32,500
How about sending those ships
to Vietnam first?

869
00:42:32,940 --> 00:42:33,870
You have no idea.

870
00:42:34,380 --> 00:42:36,190
Of all the ships, those bound for Zhoushan

871
00:42:36,190 --> 00:42:38,070
are the most needed and most urgent.

872
00:42:38,070 --> 00:42:40,870
Everything must be transported
within two weeks.

873
00:42:40,940 --> 00:42:41,670
Director Ma.

874
00:42:41,980 --> 00:42:44,110
What can be more urgent
than my matter?

875
00:42:44,570 --> 00:42:45,650
What can be more important

876
00:42:45,650 --> 00:42:47,980
than the lives of 30,000 soldiers?

877
00:42:52,380 --> 00:42:53,000
Sir,

878
00:42:53,570 --> 00:42:54,840
you have a point.

879
00:42:58,530 --> 00:43:00,030
But Chief Zhou also said

880
00:43:00,380 --> 00:43:02,500
that this shipment of military supplies

881
00:43:02,500 --> 00:43:03,800
is a top priority.

